flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> S1[SQL: SELECT Maschinen.Name, SUM(Kosten) AS gesamt]
    S1 --> S2[FROM Maschinen<br/>INNER JOIN Wartungen<br/>ON Maschinen.Maschinen_ID = Wartungen.Maschinen_ID]
    S2 --> S3[GROUP BY Maschinen.Maschinen_ID]
    S3 --> S4[ORDER BY gesamt DESC]
    S4 --> S5[LIMIT 1]
    S5 --> E[cursor.execute SQL]
    E --> F[zeile = cursor.fetchone]
    F --> R{zeile is None?}
    R -->|ja| N[return None]
    R -->|nein| T[return tuple zeile]
    N --> Ende([Ende])
    T --> Ende
